## {YYYY-MM-DD} — Adopted Synapse Arrows Playbook 4-File Structure
CONTEXT: This project did not have explicit operating substrate. Sessions
re-derived context per visit, regressions slipped through, decisions weren't
auditable.
DECISION: Adopt the 4-file structure (GOALS / STATE / DECISIONS / HEALTH) +
BOUNDARIES.md from https://github.com/michielinksee/synapse-arrows-playbook .
Every Claude session reads STATE → GOALS → recall("{PROJECT_NAME}") on entry.
REASON: Per Synapse Arrows infrastructure-first principle. Cost of adoption
~30 min; cost of NOT adopting (per measured precedent) is 1-2 weeks of
detail-iteration tax per product.
REVERSIBILITY: High — files are markdown, can be removed if the team wants.
COMMITS: {first commit SHA after adoption}
OPEN: First STATE.md update; populate `06-projects/{project}.md` in the
Playbook repo with a pointer back to this project.

